<p>A friend's loss is a personal loss, and words of comfort can strengthen bonds during difficult times.  These messages acknowledge shared experiences and offer support to a grieving friend.</p>
<li>I am so heartbroken to hear about the passing of your mother.</li>
<li>I will always remember your mother's kindness and warmth.</li>
<li> She was a truly special woman.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending my love.</li>
<li> I'm here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li> May your memories bring you peace.</li>
<li> Your mother's legacy will live on through you.</li>
<li> So sorry for your loss.</li>
<li> I'm keeping you and your family in my thoughts.</li>
<li>I offer my deepest sympathy.</li>
<li>May her memory be for a blessing.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort.</li>
<li> I can only imagine how difficult this time must be.</li>
<li> Your mother was a remarkable person.</li>
<li> Please accept my sincerest condolences.</li>
    

